cat << EOF
GGZ Gaming Zone core client libraries provides the common procedures and
utilities required to run the GGZ client and games.  The routines are
shared by other modules in order to ease coding and promote
compatibility and stability.

The core client libraries is only one part of the GGZ Gaming Zone client
setup.  Additional modules are required in the following order:

- ggz-gtk-client     OR ggz-kde-client
- ggz-gtk-games      OR ggz-kde-games
new! ggz-gnome-games && ggz-sdl-games
EOF

